Model.BugReport.PerformanceMetrics

Class MetricsComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.BugReport.PerformanceMetrics.MetricsComponent

  • public class MetricsComponent
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing a metrics component object. A performance metric usually consists of a number of metrics components, each denoting a certain skill in the title, and an array list with information holders about a certain skill.
